Developer Terms of Use
des:
BARBRI voice is an elearning application developed by BARBRI as a tool to assist students in learning and retaining various parts of the law.

Right now, the application generates a randomly-ordered rule element or practical application quiz for 34 different torts.

To use BARBRI Voice, just say "Alexa, open BARBRI Voice" and follow the instructions in the app.
